  "key_patterns": [
    "Advisory hierarchy: PartialSecurityAdvisory <- SecurityAdvisory <- IgnoredSecurityAdvisory (3-level inheritance)",
    "Platform filter strategy pattern: PlatformRequirementFilterInterface with 3 implementations (IgnoreAll, IgnoreNothing, IgnoreList)",
    "PlatformRequirementFilterFactory is a static factory selecting strategy based on bool|array input",
    "Auditor is an orchestrator: fetches advisories from RepositorySet, uses FilterListAuditor for filter auditing, returns bitmask of STATUS_* flags",
    "FilterListConfig is a value object built from composer config; getOperationConfig() returns filtered copy for 'audit'|'block' scope",
    "UnfilteredPackage supports 'all'|'block'|'audit' apply scope with package name regex + semver constraint matching",
    "FilterListAuditor builds a map of [packageName][listName][] => FilterListEntry, then matches against UnfilteredPackage exceptions",
    "Runtime is a thin wrapper/abstraction over PHP runtime introspection (constants, functions, classes, extensions)"
  ],
  "important_notes": "Auditor.audit() returns int bitmask (STATUS_OK=0, STATUS_VULNERABLE=1, STATUS_ABANDONED=2, STATUS_FILTERED=4). FORMAT_SUMMARY uses optimized partial advisory loading. IgnoredSecurityAdvisory.ignoreReason is omitted from JSON output if null. IgnoreListPlatformRequirementFilter supports '+' suffix on package name for upper-bound-only ignoring.",
